EN: I don't want you to endure any harm.

ZH: 这个孩子承受了太多的饥饿和贫困。
EN: This child has endured too much hunger and poverty.

ZH: 她已经承受了太多的折磨和虐待。
EN: She has suffered too much torment and abuse.

